HEADWORD: fax machine
<hw>fax" ma*chine`</hw> <pr>(f⟦acr⟧ks'm⟦adot⟧*sh⟦emac⟧n`)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Shortened form of <ets>telefax</ets>, from
<ets>tele-</ets> and <ets>facs</ets>imile.]</ety> <def>A device which is
designed to transmit and receive images by the facsimile{2} process.
